WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:02.000
“I felt like I’d known him forever.” 

00:02.500 --> 00:09.000
That was the first thing fashion designer Kansai Yamamoto thought after meeting Bowie. 

00:09.500 --> 00:12.000
Yamamoto, who designed these bangles, 

00:12.500 --> 00:16.500
was heavily influenced by the Japanese concept of Basara, 

00:17.000 --> 00:21.000
meaning 'extravagance and eccentricity'.